完投訴信，大家尚有另一重要任務！去撐🖐️☝️黃金周活動。<br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處：清算師團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=0ace5c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vendettists\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvendettists&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=442e7b46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vendettists</a><br />\n<br />\n#專業清算師<br />\n#民間清算師<br />\n#一鍵投訴<br />\n#碧水新村<br />\n#兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n#勿忘初衷勿被帶風<br />\n#不分化不篤灰不割蓆<br />\n#直至煲底相見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=134963588120835&amp;id=104015014549026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D134963588120835%26id%3D104015014549026&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw14uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=a5452683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=134963588120835&amp;id=104015014549026</a>"},{"pid":"2b00b4a4d54282a2f32a4848b84ae678d080077b","tid":1997232,"uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"584abb18e544dd608758cccdc03a617cfe380080","tid":1997232,"uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6faa86933fcfd3e92168b0e6df7511e408ca56b8","tid":1997232,"uid":14494,"like":376,"dislike":0,"score":376,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"方丈都出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOPjGn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOPjGn7.jpg&h=1dab870f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"圖都唔使改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\